description: Full planning application for the demolition of all buildings to enable a mixed use redevelopment of four new blocks ranging in height from five (5) to six (6) storeys (with some single storey elements) to provide 15,768sqm of floorspace (GIA), comprising: 6308 sqm of commercial space (Use Classes B1c, B2 and B8), 110 residential units including affordable housing (Use Class C3) and associated open space, amenity areas, vehicular access, accessible parking, cycle parking and refuse/recycling stores
